<HEADLINE> Hainan Province Lists Projects for Investment </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HAIKOU, October 22 (Xinhua) -- The government of southernmost
China's Hainan Province has listed 100 scientific and
technological projects open for investment in an effort to give
impetus to local economic and social development, official sources
said today.
</P>
<P>
