<HEADLINE> Foreign Investors For Southern Chinese Bonded Zone </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
GUANGZHOU, October 22 (Xinhua) -- The city of Zhuhai in south
China's Guangdong province is becoming more attractive to foreign
investors as the return of Macao to the mainland approaches.
</P>
<P>
The 3-sq km Zhuhai Bonded Zone is the largest of the six in
Guangdong. Although it is still at a preliminary stage, it has
already got a dozen overseas investment projects, involving a
billion Hong Kong dollars.
