to get investment from multinationals, he said, adding that the
zone will try to play the role of a bridge between the mainland
and the outside world.
</P>
<P>
At present, negotiations are underway for the establishment of
more than 20 foreign investment projects in the bonded zone for
infrastructure, electronics, medicines, and packing materials.
