<HEADLINE> Quality Management Research Institute Opens in Shanghai </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
SHANGHAI, October 22 (Xinhua) -- The Shanghai Juram Quality
Science Research Institute, the first facility of its kind in
China, recently opened in Shanghai, the nation's major commercial
and financial center.
</P>
<P>
The institute, jointly funded by the Juram Research Institute
in the United States and the Shanghai Quality Management Society,
will introduce advanced quality management theory and managerial
expertise.
</P>
<P>
Establishment of the institute will promote China's efforts to
integrate quality inspection with international practicers, and
provide domestic enterprises with first-rate quality inspection
training, consulting, research and appraisals.  
</P>
