Having won numerous awards since his victory in the 1959 Hong
Kong Open, Lu is the best known professional golfer from Chinese
Taipei. He stunned the world in 1971 when he finished runner-up
by just one stroke to champion Lee Trevino at the British Open.
</P>
<P>
To celebrate the Open's 40th anniversary when the Perrir Hong
Kong Open is held November 26-29 this year, there will be a
world-class field featuring professionals from the United States,
Europe and Asia. Among the star players due for the event are
