<HEADLINE> Gold Price in Hong Kong Down </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HONG KONG, October 22 (Xinhua) -- The gold price in Hong Kong
dropped 24 HK dollars to close at 2,710 HK dollars a tael on
Thursday, according to Po Sang Bank, one of the major gold dealers
in Hong Kong.
