<TEXT>
<P>
KUNMING, October 22 (Xinhua) -- An international conference on
cooperation between universities and enterprises, sponsored by the
Association of Asia and Pacific Universities, ended today in
Kunming, capital of southwest China's Yunnan Province.
</P>
<P>
The conference passed the "Kunming Declaration," stressing the
further increase in cooperation between universities and
enterprises and the industrialization of scientific and
technological findings.
</P>
