<HEADLINE> Istanbul Stock Exchange Index Down </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ANKARA, October 22 (Xinhua) -- Turkey's Istanbul Stock
Exchange National-100 Index closed at 2,210.21 points on Thursday,
down 16.22 points, or 0.69 percent, from Wednesday's finish.
</P>
<P>
The Trading was active with the turnover reaching over 73
trillion Turkish Liras (about 264 million U.S. dollars).
</P>
<P>
The financial index went down 46.59 points, or 1.64 percent, to
close at 2,682.95 points; the service index fell 22.75 points, or
0.67 percent, to close at 3,210.80 points; while the industrial
index rose 13.02 points, or 0.80 percent, to close at 1,752.40
points. 
</P>
</TEXT>
