<HEADLINE> Urgent:  Yugoslav Albanian Leader welcomes Milosevic-Holbrooke Accord </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>

<P>
BELGRADE, October 22 (Xinhua) -- Ibrahim Rugova, leader of
Yugoslavia's Albanian ethnics, on Thursday welcomed for the first
time the accord on Kosovo reached between the Yugoslav President
Slobodan Milosevic and U.S. envoy Richard Holbrooke. 
